thread.title: unfindable setting

comments.text: when you set yourself to "unfindable" in the me menu's "..." dialog, your current area will not appear next to you in people's friends list, so they can't directly teleport to you.
when you're unfindable, you also won't appear named on in.anyland.com (which lists people currently on).
